How to initialize the poti library:

poti_init (0, 0, POTI_TEXTUAL_OUTPUT) - for the standard output
poti_init (0, 0, POTI_BINARY_OUTPUT)  - for the binary output, outputs to file rastro-5-5.rst
poti_init (0, 0, POTI_TEXTUAL_BINARY_OUTPUT) - for both outputs.

poti_init (0, 0, 0) - works with pj_dump, pajeng, viva and all tools relying on libpaje
poti_init (1, 0, 0) - works with the development version of ViTE
poti_init (1, 1, 0) - works with ViTE 1.2
